trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencyDatabase" /> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.

The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection> uses the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection> to programmatically access and modify the `databases` element of the `sqlCacheDependency` in the `cache` configuration section.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection> 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection> 프로그래밍 방식으로 액세스 하 고 수정 하는 `databases` 의 요소는 `sqlCacheDependency` 에 `cache` 구성 섹션입니다.
